item.title: By: Lacey
item.dc:creator: Lacey
item.description: Very good sar bear, I've heard nothing but great thing about those rubber band thing too I'm a clippy and thick black rb girl too!!! Twinsies!! I know what I'm about to say you won't give two hoots about but any fake tanners out there will love me to death! I love fake tanners I live to far away from salons and am to lazy to always go so I use lotions yes they stink and streak but no longer! I buy tanwise self tanner $10 at Sally's it doesn't smell to bad either and the trick is the pat on baby powder when your done it absorbs all the extra so no streaks and that icky smell is gone too!! And skin is soft and tan like a little Hawaiian baby! Oh and rub the powder around till it all feels smooth and dry :)
